Screen Name: User List
Description: Displays users with role and department context.
Navigation Path: ?route=users
User Roles Allowed: admin, hr, manager, dept_head (as per RBAC scope)
Device/Platform: Web
Responsive Behaviour: Table wraps/scrolls horizontally on smaller screens

UI Elements
Field Name | Label | Type | Control Type | Mandatory | Read Only | Default | Placeholder | Validation | Max Length | Format | Tooltip | Remarks
search | Search Users | text | input | No | No | blank | Name/role/department | Optional filter | 100 | string | Quick filter | Server-side filter
role_filter | Role | enum | dropdown | No | No | all | Select role | Optional | 50 | enum | Role filter | RBAC-safe options
department_filter | Department | int | dropdown | No | No | all | Select department | Optional | 11 | integer | Dept filter | Scoped by user role
user_grid | User List | data | table | NA | Yes | loaded | NA | Read-only grid | NA | tabular | User records | Includes action column

Layout & Sections
Header: Standard app header
Footer: Standard app footer
Sections/Panels: Filter panel, user grid, pagination
Tabs/Accordions: NA
Grid/List Details: Name, username, email, role, department, status, actions

Actions
Action | Description | Trigger | Pre-condition | Post-condition | API/Service Called | Success Message | Error Handling
Search | Filter list | Click Search/Enter | User has list access | Filtered users displayed | UserController + UserModel | NA | Empty state shown
Create User | Open create screen | Click Create | Permission available | Navigate to user create | Router | NA | Forbidden redirect
Edit User | Open edit form | Click Edit icon | Permission and valid id | User edit screen opened | Router + UserController | NA | Record not found message

Client-side Logic
Field dependencies:
- Department options depend on role scope
Dynamic enable/disable rules:
- Create/Edit action hidden if user lacks permission
Conditional visibility:
- Status badges shown when active/inactive state available

