Screen Name: Workflow Creation/Editing
Description: Create or update workflow definition with multi-step approval rules.
Navigation Path: ?route=workflows/create and ?route=workflows/edit&id={id}
User Roles Allowed: admin, finance
Device/Platform: Web
Responsive Behaviour: Multi-section form collapses to single column on mobile

UI Elements
Field Name | Label | Type | Control Type | Mandatory | Read Only | Default | Placeholder | Validation | Max Length | Format | Tooltip | Remarks
workflow_name | Workflow Name | text | input | Yes | No | blank | Enter workflow name | Required | 150 | string | Workflow title | Unique preferred
workflow_type | Request Type | enum | dropdown | Yes | No | expense | Select type | Valid enum | 20 | enum | Applies to request type | expense/purchase/other
min_amount | Min Amount | decimal | input | No | No | 0.00 | Enter min amount | Numeric | 15,2 | decimal | Lower bound | Optional
max_amount | Max Amount | decimal | input | No | No | blank | Enter max amount | Numeric and >= min | 15,2 | decimal | Upper bound | Optional
step_definitions | Approval Steps | object | repeatable rows | Yes | No | blank | Add approver step | At least one step required | NA | structured | Step setup | role/user/dept_head mode
is_active | Active | bool | toggle | No | No | true | NA | Boolean | 1 | boolean | Enable workflow | Defaults active

Layout & Sections
Header: Standard app header
Footer: Standard app footer
Sections/Panels: Workflow details, approval step builder, status settings
Tabs/Accordions: Optional accordion for each step
Grid/List Details: Step No, Approver Mode, Target, Conditions, Timeout, Required

Actions
Action | Description | Trigger | Pre-condition | Post-condition | API/Service Called | Success Message | Error Handling
Add Step | Add new approval step | Click Add Step | Workflow form open | New step row added | Client-side + WorkflowController validation | Step added | Invalid step warning
Save Workflow | Create/update workflow | Click Save | Required fields and valid steps | Workflow persisted | WorkflowController + WorkflowModel | Workflow saved successfully | Validation error list
Cancel | Exit without save | Click Cancel | NA | Return to workflow list | Router | NA | Safe fallback

Client-side Logic
Field dependencies:
- Max amount must be greater than or equal to min amount
- Step target required based on approver mode
Dynamic enable/disable rules:
- Save disabled if no valid step definitions
Conditional visibility:
- User picker shown only when approver mode is user
- Role picker shown only when approver mode is role

