Screen Name: Expanse Request
Description: Creates and reviews an individual expense request with workflow actions.
Navigation Path: ?route=expenses/create and ?route=expenses/review&id={id}
User Roles Allowed: employee (create), manager/dept_head/finance/admin/hr (review as per RBAC)
Device/Platform: Web
Responsive Behaviour: Form and review panels stack on smaller screens

UI Elements
Field Name | Label | Type | Control Type | Mandatory | Read Only | Default | Placeholder | Validation | Max Length | Format | Tooltip | Remarks
request_reference_no | Reference No | text | read-only label | NA | Yes | auto-generated | NA | System generated | 30 | string | Unique reference | Visible after create
request_type | Request Type | enum | dropdown/label | Yes | Conditional | expense | Select type | Valid enum | 20 | enum | Type | Read-only in review mode
request_amount | Amount | decimal | input/label | Yes | Conditional | blank | 0.00 | Positive value | 15,2 | decimal | Requested amount | Workflow rule input
attachments | Attachments | file/data | upload + list | No | Conditional | blank | Upload document | Type/size checks | NA | binary/list | Supporting files | View/download supported
review_action | Approver Action | enum | buttons/dropdown | Yes (review) | No | pending | Select action | approve/reject/reassign | 20 | enum | Workflow action | Available in review mode
action_comment | Comment | text | textarea | Conditional | No | blank | Enter decision remarks | Required for reject/reassign (policy) | 1000 | string | Approval note | Saved in action history

Layout & Sections
Header: Standard app header
Footer: Standard app footer
Sections/Panels: Request details, budget/workflow context, attachment panel, action panel
Tabs/Accordions: Optional tabs for details/history/attachments
Grid/List Details: Action history grid for previous steps

Actions
Action | Description | Trigger | Pre-condition | Post-condition | API/Service Called | Success Message | Error Handling
Submit Request | Save new request | Click Submit | Required fields valid | Request created with pending status | ExpenseController + ExpenseModel | Request submitted successfully | Validation error message
Approve/Reject/Reassign | Process workflow decision | Click action button | User is current approver and authorized | Request step/status updated and action logged | ExpenseController + WorkflowModel | Action recorded successfully | Unauthorized/invalid state error
View Attachment | Open attachment stream | Click attachment name | Authorized access | Attachment displayed/downloaded | ExpenseController attachment endpoints | NA | Attachment not found/forbidden

Client-side Logic
Field dependencies:
- Review action controls comment requirement and reassignee fields
Dynamic enable/disable rules:
- Action buttons disabled when request is already final
Conditional visibility:
- Action panel visible only for authorized approvers in review mode

